{"article_id":"qzCJijgdMqjn4r0T","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Speaking at a rally in Phoenix ,","depth":3},{"id":1,"text":"president attempts to counter widespread , bipartisan condemnation of his response to far-right violence","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"Donald Trump has sought to portray himself as the true victim of the deadly events in Charlottesville ,","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"launching an all-out assault on the media","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"and branding journalists","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"who \" do not like our country \"","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"as the true source of division in America .","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"Protests at Donald Trump rally in Phoenix - in pictures","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"Read more","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"At a rally in Phoenix , evocative of his populist election campaign , the US president attacked coverage of his response to the white supremacist violence","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"and complained bitterly to his audience about how he had been treated .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"He re-read three statements","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"he made in the wake of the tragedy","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"and ,","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"deploying authoritarian rhetoric ,","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"declared :","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"\" It ' s time","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"to expose the crooked media deceptions","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"and to challenge the media for their role","depth":11},{"id":19,"text":"in fomenting divisions","depth":11},{"id":20,"text":"and yes , by the way , they are trying to take away our history and our heritage. \"","depth":9},{"id":21,"text":"The crowd","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"- some scowling ,","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"some laughing -","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"turned and jeered at journalists in the media enclosure","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"and chanted :","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"\" CNN sucks !","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"CNN sucks ! \"","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"Even as he spoke","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"protesters outside the Phoenix Convention Center had gathered","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"to voice anger at his presence .","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"Police used smoke bombs and teargas on the crowds","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"after plastic bottles were reportedly thrown .","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"The rally was the latest example of Trump as a Jekyll and Hyde public performer ,","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"coming just 24 hours after a sober speech to the military","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"setting out future strategy in Afghanistan .","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"On Tuesday he was back in his element , pugnacious and freewheeling ,","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"throwing red meat to an eager crowd .","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"The arena ,","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"which has a capacity of 19,000 ,","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"was mostly full of people","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"waving signs","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"saying","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"\" Drain the swamp \" ,","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"\" Make America proud again \" and \" Women for Trump \" .","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"Quick guide","depth":2},{"id":46,"text":"What happened at the Charlottesville protests ?","depth":5},{"id":47,"text":"Show Hide","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"What happened in Charlottesville on 12 August ?","depth":5},{"id":49,"text":"White nationalists gathered in Charlottesville , Virginia ,","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"to protest against a plan","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"to remove a statue of Robert E Lee , the Confederacy ' s top general in the American civil war .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"Demonstrators chanted racist statements ,","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"carried antisemitic placards","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"and held torches during the \" Unite the Right \" rally ,","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"which was organised by white nationalist Jason Kessler .","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"The march was met by anti-fascist demonstrators ,","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"and some skirmishes broke out","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"before James Fields , 20 , allegedly ploughed a car into a group of counter-demonstrators .","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"Civil rights activist Heather Heyer , 32 , died","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"and others were injured .","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"Fields has been charged with murder .","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"The president caused outrage","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"when , in a chaotic press conference at Trump Tower , he blamed \" both sides \" for the carnage in Charlottesville .","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"On Tuesday night he insisted","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"that he had in fact condemned hatred , bigotry and violence as well as neo-Nazis , white supremacists and the Ku Klux Klan .","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"Play Video 0:52","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"Protests erupt after Trump ' s rally in Arizona - video","depth":7},{"id":68,"text":"He took his first statement on Charlottesville from his pocket","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"and told his audience :","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"\" You know where my heart is .","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"I ' m really doing this","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"to show you","depth":13},{"id":73,"text":"how damned dishonest these people are ...","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"I don ' t want to bore you with this","depth":12},{"id":75,"text":"but it shows you how dishonest they are . \"","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"Trump proceeded to read out the remarks to polite applause ,","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"although he failed to repeat the inflammatory words","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"he had used","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"when he blamed \" both sides \" .","depth":13},{"id":80,"text":"He repeatedly broke off from his teleprompter","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"to call out \" the failing New York Times \" and Washington Post ,","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"which he branded \" a lobbying tool for Amazon \" .","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"Amazon ' s founder , Jeff Bezos , bought the Post","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"but the entities have no relationship .","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"But it was","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"when the president mentioned CNN","depth":14},{"id":87,"text":"- \" which is so bad and so pathetic","depth":15},{"id":88,"text":"and their ratings are going down \" -","depth":15},{"id":89,"text":"that the crowd booed loudly","depth":14},{"id":90,"text":"and burst into a chorus of","depth":15},{"id":91,"text":"\" CNN sucks ! \"","depth":15},{"id":92,"text":"Trump even made reference to the former CNN contributor Jeffrey Lord ,","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"who was fired","depth":14},{"id":94,"text":"for tweeting the Nazi salute \" Sieg Heil \" at a liberal activist .","depth":14},{"id":95,"text":"\" Poor Jeffrey , \"","depth":14},{"id":96,"text":"the president said .","depth":14},{"id":97,"text":"\" I guess","depth":15},{"id":98,"text":"he was getting a little bit fed up","depth":16},{"id":99,"text":"and was probably fighting back too hard","depth":16},{"id":100,"text":"and they said ,","depth":15},{"id":101,"text":"' We got ta get out of here . ' \"","depth":15},{"id":102,"text":"The president also mocked the protesters outside ,","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"claiming","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"the turnout against Tuesday ' s rally was lower than expected .","depth":13},{"id":105,"text":"He returned to a theme of moral equivalence","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"for which he was criticised in the wake of Charlottesville :","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"\" You know ,","depth":14},{"id":108,"text":"they show up in the helmets and the black masks .","depth":15},{"id":109,"text":"They ' ve got clubs","depth":16},{"id":110,"text":"and they ' ve got everything .","depth":16},{"id":111,"text":"\" Antifa ! \"","depth":15},{"id":112,"text":"he shouted -","depth":15},{"id":113,"text":"a term","depth":15},{"id":114,"text":"used to describe anti-fascist groups .","depth":15},{"id":115,"text":"In a drawn-out performance piece , Trump read out his second and third pronouncements in the aftermath of Charlottesville ,","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"while throwing in","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"that he lives \" in a bigger , more beautiful apartment \" than the elites","depth":12},{"id":118,"text":"aligned against him ,","depth":12},{"id":119,"text":"\" and I live in the White House too \" .","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"Then came perhaps his key line :","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"\" The media can attack me","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"but where I draw the line is when they attack you ,","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"which is what they do ,","depth":12},{"id":124,"text":"when they attack the decency of our supporters .","depth":12},{"id":125,"text":"You are honest , hard-working , taxpaying Americans","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"- and by the way , you ' re overtaxed ,","depth":13},{"id":127,"text":"but we ' re going to get your taxes down -","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"who love our nation ,","depth":12},{"id":129,"text":"obey our laws","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"and care for our people . \"","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"It ' s time","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"to expose the crooked media deceptions","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"and to challenge the media for their role","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"in fomenting divisions","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"and yes , by the way , they are trying to take away our history and our heritage .","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"You see that .","depth":12},{"id":137,"text":"These are truly dishonest people .","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"Not all of them .","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"You have some very good reporters ,","depth":14},{"id":140,"text":"you have some very fair journalists .","depth":14},{"id":141,"text":"But for the most part , these are really , really dishonest people .","depth":13},{"id":142,"text":"\" They ' re bad people","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"and I really think","depth":14},{"id":144,"text":"they don ' t like our country .","depth":14},{"id":145,"text":"I really believe that .","depth":13},{"id":146,"text":"And I don ' t believe","depth":15},{"id":147,"text":"they ' re going to change","depth":15},{"id":148,"text":"and that ' s why I do this .","depth":14},{"id":149,"text":"If they would change ,","depth":14},{"id":150,"text":"I would never say it .","depth":14},{"id":151,"text":"The only people","depth":14},{"id":152,"text":"giving a platform to these hate groups","depth":14},{"id":153,"text":"is the media itself and the fake news . \"","depth":13},{"id":154,"text":"Trump then mocked the cameras in the arena ,","depth":10},{"id":155,"text":"claiming","depth":11},{"id":156,"text":"they were turning off their red lights","depth":12},{"id":157,"text":"and stopping live coverage .","depth":12},{"id":158,"text":"\" These are sick people .","depth":10},{"id":159,"text":"You would think","depth":13},{"id":160,"text":"they want to make our country great again","depth":13},{"id":161,"text":"and I honestly believe","depth":13},{"id":162,"text":"they don ' t .","depth":13},{"id":163,"text":"If you want to discover the source of the division in our country ,","depth":12},{"id":164,"text":"look no further than the fake news and the crooked media ,","depth":13},{"id":165,"text":"which would rather get ratings and clicks","depth":14},{"id":166,"text":"than tell the truth . \"","depth":14},{"id":167,"text":"The crowd turned around several times","depth":9},{"id":168,"text":"to boo and shout epithets at the media .","depth":9},{"id":169,"text":"The tactic was similar to Trump ' s last rally in West Virginia ,","depth":9},{"id":170,"text":"when he sought to blame Democrats for the investigation into his campaign ' s alleged collusion with Russia ,","depth":11},{"id":171,"text":"and cast it as an attack on his own supporters .","depth":11},{"id":172,"text":"But he went on to praise conservative Fox News","depth":11},{"id":173,"text":"for \" treating me fairly \" .","depth":11},{"id":174,"text":"Earlier , speakers at the rally had included the housing secretary , Ben Carson ,","depth":8},{"id":175,"text":"who is African American ,","depth":8},{"id":176,"text":"and Alveda King , the niece of the civil rights leader Martin Luther King Jr .","depth":7},{"id":177,"text":"Prominent behind the speakers was an African American man","depth":7},{"id":178,"text":"wearing a T-shirt","depth":8},{"id":179,"text":"that said :","depth":9},{"id":180,"text":"' Trump & Republicans are not racist . '","depth":9},{"id":181,"text":"During his sprawling 75-minute speech , the president turned to illegal immigration , a major issue for his base in Arizona .","depth":7},{"id":182,"text":"He dropped a clear hint","depth":10},{"id":183,"text":"that he intends to pardon Joe Arpaio , the former sheriff of Maricopa county , over his conviction","depth":11},{"id":184,"text":"for breaking the law with immigration patrols .","depth":11},{"id":185,"text":"He asked :","depth":11},{"id":186,"text":"\" Do the people in this room like Sheriff Joe ? \"","depth":11},{"id":187,"text":"There was a roar from the crowd and chants of \" Pardon Joe ! \"","depth":11},{"id":188,"text":"Arpaio was in the crowd .","depth":11},{"id":189,"text":"Trump said :","depth":9},{"id":190,"text":"\" Was Sheriff Joe convicted","depth":12},{"id":191,"text":"for doing his job ?","depth":12},{"id":192,"text":"He should have had a jury .","depth":11},{"id":193,"text":"I ' ll make a prediction .","depth":12},{"id":194,"text":"I think","depth":13},{"id":195,"text":"he ' s going to be just fine .","depth":13},{"id":196,"text":"But I won ' t do it tonight","depth":12},{"id":197,"text":"because I don ' t want to cause any controversy . \"","depth":12},{"id":198,"text":"In another startling moment , Trump ,","depth":12},{"id":199,"text":"who hours earlier had visited the border at Yuma ,","depth":12},{"id":200,"text":"threatened to shut down the federal government","depth":11},{"id":201,"text":"unless Congress provided funding for his promised border wall .","depth":10},{"id":202,"text":"He told the rally","depth":11},{"id":203,"text":"that he had a message for \" obstructionist \" Democrats .","depth":11},{"id":204,"text":"The House has passed a spending bill with funding for the border wall","depth":12},{"id":205,"text":"but it faces an uncertain future in the Senate .","depth":12},{"id":206,"text":"\" If we have to close down our government ,","depth":15},{"id":207,"text":"we ' re building that wall , \"","depth":15},{"id":208,"text":"he said .","depth":14},{"id":209,"text":"\" We ' re going to have our wall .","depth":13},{"id":210,"text":"The American people voted for immigration control .","depth":13},{"id":211,"text":"We ' re going to get that wall . \"","depth":13},{"id":212,"text":"Trump accused Democrats of putting US security at risk","depth":10},{"id":213,"text":"by not supporting the proposal , one of his most popular campaign promises .","depth":10},{"id":214,"text":"The crowd erupted in cries of :","depth":10},{"id":215,"text":"\" Build that wall ! \"","depth":10},{"id":216,"text":"Trump also took swipes at Arizona ' s two senators , Jeff Flake and John McCain ,","depth":10},{"id":217,"text":"who have criticised him .","depth":10},{"id":218,"text":"He said","depth":11},{"id":219,"text":"that after his well-received address on Monday , he was told :","depth":13},{"id":220,"text":"\" Please , please Mr President , don ' t mention any names .","depth":13},{"id":221,"text":"So I won ' t . \"","depth":12},{"id":222,"text":"He continued :","depth":11},{"id":223,"text":"\" I will not mention any names","depth":13},{"id":224,"text":"- very presidential .","depth":13},{"id":225,"text":"And nobody wants me to mention your other senator","depth":16},{"id":226,"text":"[ Flake ] ,","depth":16},{"id":227,"text":"who ' s weak on border , weak on crime .","depth":15},{"id":228,"text":"Nobody knows","depth":15},{"id":229,"text":"who the hell he is !","depth":15},{"id":230,"text":"See ,","depth":15},{"id":231,"text":"I haven ' t mentioned any names ,","depth":15},{"id":232,"text":"so now everybody ' s happy . \"","depth":14},{"id":233,"text":"On a night","depth":11},{"id":234,"text":"when he had brought his verbal machine gun ,","depth":11},{"id":235,"text":"Trump also took aim at the Nafta trade deal with Canada and Mexico ,","depth":11},{"id":236,"text":"which is being renegotiated .","depth":11},{"id":237,"text":"\" Personally , I don ' t think","depth":12},{"id":238,"text":"we can make a deal , \"","depth":12},{"id":239,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":240,"text":"\" I think","depth":11},{"id":241,"text":"we ' ll end up probably terminating Nafta at some point . \"","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":483,"left":286,"right":482,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":286,"left":243,"right":285,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":243,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":285,"left":273,"right":284,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":273,"left":249,"right":272,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":249,"left":248,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":248,"left":247,"right":7,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":247,"left":2,"right":246,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":246,"left":3,"right":245,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":245,"left":244,"right":6,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":244,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":272,"left":260,"right":271,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":260,"left":250,"right":259,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":250,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":259,"left":251,"right":258,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":251,"left":11,"right":12